{"id": "f72fadcf6e4b82f73b0ac880e84671b73caa73c8a42051f394dd115a947caf67", "item_id": "489600d673:0", "text": "PxrRandomTextureManifold with PxrMultiTexture to assign random textures to many objects:"}
{"id": "16a1206176400144c137f1555c96f0ea547c93623fd1e2a3e9c7fb4379d85b7e", "item_id": "489600d673:1", "text": "Randomly assign up to 10 textures to a group of objects."}
{"id": "7447527a737c4b56570784a7a334468a8bc162e689064267f685dd6b35128c65", "item_id": "489600d673:2", "text": "Randomize the texture orientations and offsets."}
{"id": "00a7823c6b42c14cf7bb1f2fd2d49db7ad9a137a5dea61609f2b3ba6b3a966a8", "item_id": "489600d673:3", "text": "Assign textures by setting the value of a primitive variable (see"}
{"id": "78ec793702a90feff66a3e717919f8412bef12af154d2e38cba201bc78af7dd7", "item_id": "489600d673:74", "text": "Adding the textureID primvar in Maya"}
{"id": "37a6013ec9439abb986010d4bfd81d944144fb461001224aa875eecc982d0ba4", "item_id": "489600d673:5", "text": "PxrRandomTextureManifold can only be used with"}
{"id": "9ae2347670686481700f49f3a1c4674060684d86bd495b4dfc1617426f7f64a8", "item_id": "489600d673:6", "text": "PxrMultiTexture"}
{"id": "a450afa45220562659272138e3ac03e6fa8df812be7f181efe89303764f177cb", "item_id": "489600d673:9", "text": "Number of Textures"}
{"id": "caf0d9c09dad0f6de6d31c7904202d9c58d4904d2a1d6731c5f27b011dfa944d", "item_id": "489600d673:10", "text": "The number of texture you want to use. You should have at least one texture and PxrMultiTexture supports up to 10 textures."}
{"id": "6be86eadbf0ce307cb75488915f5662e9d60a93075880359ed7a3c85d46b8bfe", "item_id": "489600d673:11", "text": "Texture Order"}
{"id": "731b4219fb7383521a48fbd3851066e44d718014bb38baaa8079cd8ceeef42c9", "item_id": "489600d673:12", "text": "The order in which PxrMultiTexture will assign its textures to the objects."}
{"id": "8e37953d23daca5ff01b8282c33f4e0a2152f1d1885f94c06418617e3ee1d24e", "item_id": "489600d673:35", "text": "Value"}
{"id": "5e23ec6a300dc60a79641769017e16e9bf042cbd8fd0a54586a048ab9da972ff", "item_id": "489600d673:14", "text": "Mode"}
{"id": "007877479e2173b20d7a60df177ccce8cb2db376f63cf42f9b2d5c221444a376", "item_id": "489600d673:16", "text": "Ordered"}
{"id": "87dfedc137c35b89eb25331000ba4dd2434c3433ee8946fd55b850bb59a9440d", "item_id": "489600d673:17", "text": "Textures ordered based on the random source. The number will wrap in the 0->numTextures"}
{"id": "2269c0be009b610cfdbb8cfe9253ad37cf95062fb3f5a7560268ff259ea9f087", "item_id": "489600d673:18", "text": "range"}
{"id": "acd8c4ee850c8291065dc8197ad7c6782b5e5281c026298ea1d5501e4fabebd3", "item_id": "489600d673:20", "text": "When using the"}
{"id": "270b86031b1b7ae9a36145cae0bfd63ac548101b56e5e0f43ea9a04668b53f08", "item_id": "489600d673:21", "text": "textureID PrimVar, the texture index will match the primvar."}
{"id": "67bc484430fe87babe3c35d2ba4827d029f1c7e415a92de44885a9c88536661f", "item_id": "489600d673:22", "text": "Random"}
{"id": "a337df082370a9e9dbb85261a11d2edb40a55a31d73b5c3935d1c1859add3347", "item_id": "489600d673:23", "text": "Textures randomised"}
{"id": "a525c9c063291703d3c649972ca18301b63e10cc65f77b76383284acdc0962c8", "item_id": "489600d673:24", "text": "based on the random source."}
{"id": "3fe02a548e905a06498d7ed5dff92bc1a666d6180b859742cf3dccc04e8dd9fb", "item_id": "489600d673:25", "text": "Tiling"}
{"id": "248eb6d67a152ec676b530f3441b1cb77586938091de389f885258f8f686c703", "item_id": "489600d673:26", "text": "Tiling Mode"}
{"id": "fcd651b528de0724d322bdff90b085be45d8b072f00a693a11841ee38058bbc5", "item_id": "489600d673:27", "text": "Select between Regular and Hexagonal tiling modes"}
{"id": "16b6668d9831a1b8d2d003496db6a62b7f525df6c556d7c04681fbed2251c845", "item_id": "489600d673:28", "text": "Frequency"}
{"id": "65358310a3b07727f949eef48ddcea014ae63748197e3891767299a7f03706ed", "item_id": "489600d673:29", "text": "Texture frequency"}
{"id": "a4df7dbb8d57c8736434ff8cdeb6d3a4620c045f6726cc66c4f7d0c977a07327", "item_id": "489600d673:30", "text": "Blend Width"}
{"id": "05825109c388398454d3572029ed329e9a6990ab1ae2e404003218871a0aa87a", "item_id": "489600d673:31", "text": "Exponentiated blending as described by Burley"}
{"id": "1f7483c8a10473d3d369e45e15775a286449f3934eec0c370dbf46e0af413366", "item_id": "489600d673:32", "text": "Randomize"}
{"id": "d069e8002b0aa476fc2f6ade310f102a89e72cacc08da6e2b2de859a2e9003d9", "item_id": "489600d673:33", "text": "Random Source"}
{"id": "4acf3219c20b7e021e9e771db64a5a33e82eb2945820ea5d3cc027bcf1a3409b", "item_id": "489600d673:34", "text": "For each object to get a different variation, you need to select something unique about them to create a unique seed. You have a choice between the object's id, the object's name and a \"textureID\" primitive variable."}
{"id": "0e570ca6fabe24f94e52c1833f3ffd25567022beb826fa16891f3322051bc221", "item_id": "489600d673:36", "text": "Source"}
{"id": "fcb4dd842c61858a8dffb91fc365fce2203f19260b8bcfc4c100a983404973eb", "item_id": "489600d673:37", "text": "Depends on"}
{"id": "c49affcdd5345ea6e90d0d877e7017ac8e153d2d0df9a45f9a15a4d3b2ebad8c", "item_id": "489600d673:38", "text": "Object Id"}
{"id": "df9bc7bfc7f33b956dbcc76e3096e17dea346efd4f55f5bda33e76d8be875225", "item_id": "489600d673:39", "text": "Object Name"}
{"id": "5e0b523c64f5e54ffeefeaa978484482ad750ae4057d1e3df076b1e7117b5785", "item_id": "489600d673:40", "text": "textureID PrimVar"}
{"id": "afced27d4e13ce477ddf889e80d9250ea276881af8f76dacbbfd9e99dd272a0c", "item_id": "489600d673:41", "text": "The first two attributes are created by the software outputting the RIB and depending on your application (Maya, Katana, etc...), one may work better than the other."}
{"id": "38ff92080b14f1431056fd84c9d97a4343072112e36eaa1e729775bb8422f0cb", "item_id": "489600d673:42", "text": "The textureID primitive variable needs to be created on your scene shapes and set to a value between 0 and 9 (PxrMultitexture supports up to 10 textures). If this mode is selected and the primvar does not exist, the pattern will assume a value of 0, i.e. the first texture."}
{"id": "287d18467622df3f977b8a1dc22e12ad35e5024f271fe96c1f4f6b326c6f6bda", "item_id": "489600d673:43", "text": "Extra Seed"}
{"id": "6694e959b273734dae618458fac3847595448d7a170521cca4f6ae54b7b753d4", "item_id": "489600d673:44", "text": "If you want one of these patterns to compute a different variation, set the randomExtraSeed to a non-zero value. This parameter will only influence the randomization parameters (randomOrientation, randomFlipS, etc)."}
{"id": "ad8f9fee37994bbd50a0cd4afb7ffacd27e5c8ef503d05bf9024473ea120a3d4", "item_id": "489600d673:45", "text": "Random Orientation"}
{"id": "439fabe8903efd768b1929295f7c2b5421fa2c5f8f0d0005b09bd7056cf31d18", "item_id": "489600d673:46", "text": "Randomize the orientation of the textures by randomly swapping s and t."}
{"id": "4718158121fb2cec5b1839a50dcdb4a273746401d9f0d35b9c6b32d0004f08be", "item_id": "489600d673:47", "text": "Random S Flip"}
{"id": "922be1a8e7ac417a199232be39d0d1bad185236ebe9189cb3cf142b71bac992f", "item_id": "489600d673:48", "text": "Randomly flip the direction of s."}
{"id": "220e9aea516a7a45fe5c2bb5dff9c7f95c7c8760f5fdbcdf4d0a434325bc8d68", "item_id": "489600d673:49", "text": "Random T Flip"}
{"id": "7ec1d0856d0f48c41b84c3a113028ad1366fc7c18b11328287f3f9fda1525406", "item_id": "489600d673:50", "text": "Randomly flip the direction of t."}
{"id": "2e87cd67afab8c0c97a04f427e0c6f14f71bd63f2a0072ff13110a8089d03021", "item_id": "489600d673:51", "text": "Random S Offset"}
{"id": "90b01a33a2e13848986468bd91a98ecaa404e749b002bc9bbd628c41189c21d4", "item_id": "489600d673:52", "text": "Randomly offset s. You should probably avoid this if your textures are not tiling seamlessly."}
{"id": "15582bfeee8edfbccf7bf07bd8363ec008dd07b76496f1bc06d873a8904b5142", "item_id": "489600d673:53", "text": "Random T Offset"}
{"id": "76c98e52b2170acb1f963d068f51531027d47fc05329dae80a6be53bc1c69de0", "item_id": "489600d673:54", "text": "Randomly offset t. You should probably avoid this if your textures are not tiling seamlessly."}
{"id": "7598dc637d7766288323328a9bc69dbce01f1c82d603dcb9bb238087659bdcc7", "item_id": "489600d673:55", "text": "Manifold 2D"}
{"id": "1968034b13f84d0c3e441fcc8b5f3ec7b75fcabdbcecb68177445498557d3e33", "item_id": "489600d673:56", "text": "Angle"}
{"id": "751f11467c33d49fdaa1dadc5dda35332eb09fa17831247452e5d20fd3f147c2", "item_id": "489600d673:57", "text": "Global rotation angle around the origin of the st domain."}
{"id": "dfce4fe1a66ce3ba0da2f5bc8c567f5a562d9d83b7fa89c000352b073ea4a014", "item_id": "489600d673:58", "text": "Global Scale"}
{"id": "5c42bba8bbf93884288fba8d4fc0527679bb4249adcabfe24503e5f47309c491", "item_id": "489600d673:59", "text": "Scale the st domain while preserving the aspect ratio defined by scaleS and scaleT."}
{"id": "de02ff6a41bb301f28ff4320ea109951b8f00c4bdbd06a50b8b1d6b7d6546538", "item_id": "489600d673:60", "text": "Scale S"}
{"id": "2564778edb13c55c5704dbda23c55c7740547bbefc04866f22568c1597bfd1a3", "item_id": "489600d673:61", "text": "Frequency of the feature in S."}
{"id": "74ed367dd43611959a619b470a288d25878f785a729581a3ec0df16a3ae880b4", "item_id": "489600d673:62", "text": "Scale T"}
{"id": "a2289dde977d612c255d04d2aa22bcab76f76152340c97017f8d21ad50e15003", "item_id": "489600d673:63", "text": "Frequency of the feature in T"}
{"id": "79182e90c534c862c9a1371a047fc3b73fd5f5b657802cfcfd78324f778ab585", "item_id": "489600d673:64", "text": "Offset S"}
{"id": "60c39a0a6caf7f89dc14a9413b5bae5265d3b00ee10715de89f806e4b2766c34", "item_id": "489600d673:65", "text": "Offset from origin in S."}
{"id": "f25c3396d562c4c180fe177b4acefab8f7fbb413aa193189fa71a156ca5bfd7d", "item_id": "489600d673:66", "text": "Offset T"}
{"id": "90fef1d5351323e45eecc5d8d1e27b64ee864613ba47b6fa465719d47a512a20", "item_id": "489600d673:67", "text": "Offset from origin in T."}
{"id": "7b4e3156de47599b1c25274775d4aa507a2ae5e23a74591b475e50c192b5d2e5", "item_id": "489600d673:68", "text": "invert T"}
{"id": "bdcc8e9a52362a6c87e62a9a6ef6199d1ed930751caa77128f7e56872e4a1ea0", "item_id": "489600d673:69", "text": "Invert the direction of T."}
{"id": "9f67c9d4c723ae1283959412cd003591d6f42d81a2c0d7e0595fa6b3ec8942c4", "item_id": "489600d673:70", "text": "PrimVar S/ST"}
{"id": "d31d863c6937c847e07b1befac39f36d6075b41d3439f4513cbf6ce9ba5b0aa4", "item_id": "489600d673:71", "text": "Name of custom 1D S or 2D ST primvar."}
{"id": "ff6decb98de33f019292f6f4ff9f2e2afa4aac8f87a3fffd33365b3fcd630822", "item_id": "489600d673:72", "text": "PrimVar T"}
{"id": "b6110b12756c83957293a5ef6710b1ee8d3460b15b726d4690e4db2c8d932fc8", "item_id": "489600d673:73", "text": "Name of custom 1D T primvar."}
{"id": "c9438fbed10363faae87b7166d415d93388c4f6aa04e738e5636ea99b331eb3a", "item_id": "489600d673:75", "text": "Using MEL"}
{"id": "0fc587109dd2a0bcc3827ff10921fc9df1a49850d9aa360b20939f6bd2c889ed", "item_id": "489600d673:76", "text": "Select the objects you want to add the primvar to and run the MEL below."}
{"id": "998a2cbb34edec2c34e525ffa027d675dcc2a40e43926adf4e113fdc1f09ae3f", "item_id": "489600d673:77", "text": "The \""}
{"id": "e7f99cae82fcd5d03846388b70e90ff10c8461e9a01da71ff9f4d4bbe78ccf41", "item_id": "489600d673:78", "text": "will appear in the channel box and the attribute editor so you can set its value and will be exported by RFM as the expected \""}
{"id": "23eb667fac0f582eec1f8db5aa8c3e9133f2dc591964c8733688dfec84558dd7", "item_id": "489600d673:79", "text": "primvar."}
